WEBVTT

1
00:01:18.184 --> 00:01:21.620
A hundred years ago.
all was right with our world.

2
00:01:21.754 --> 00:01:24.723
Prosperity and peace filled our days.

3
00:01:24.857 --> 00:01:26.381
The Four Nations:

4
00:01:26.526 --> 00:01:32.362
Water. Earth. Fire and Air Nomads
lived amongst each other in harmony.

5
00:01:32.498 --> 00:01:37.231
Great respect was afforded to all those
who could bend their natural element.

6
00:01:37.370 --> 00:01:41.363
The Avatar was the only person
born amongst all the nations

7
00:01:41.507 --> 00:01:44.237
who could master all four elements.

8
00:01:44.377 --> 00:01:48.313
He was the only one who could
communicate with the Spirit World.

9
00:01:48.448 --> 00:01:52.976
With the Spirits'guidance.
the Avatar kept balance in the world.

10
00:01:53.786 --> 00:01:57.722
And then. a hundred years ago.
he just disappeared.

11
00:02:34.427 --> 00:02:36.361
I'm sorry. I'm sorry!

12
00:02:36.496 --> 00:02:38.464
Hey. I'm sorry.
I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry!

13
00:02:38.598 --> 00:02:42.557
I'm sorry! I'm sorry! Hey!
It Worked better that time.

14
00:02:42.702 --> 00:02:46.160
I thought about Mom. Isn't that strange?

15
00:02:47.440 --> 00:02:50.432
Yeah. I guess so.

16
00:02:50.776 --> 00:02:55.042
Just stop doing that stuff around me.
I alWays get Wet.

17
00:02:58.618 --> 00:03:01.644
My brother and I live
in the Southern Water Tribe.

18
00:03:01.787 --> 00:03:06.383
which was once a big city.
Our father is off fighting in The War.

19
00:03:06.726 --> 00:03:09.854
My mother was taken prisoner
and killed when I was young.

20
00:03:10.530 --> 00:03:13.988
In this time of war. food is scarce.

21
00:03:14.133 --> 00:03:16.294
My brother and I often
go hunting for food.

22
00:03:16.435 --> 00:03:20.633
but. unfortunately. my brother
isn't the best hunter in the world.

23
00:03:25.311 --> 00:03:27.472
- Tiger seal.
- Are you sure?

24
00:03:51.237 --> 00:03:52.829
I did everything Dad said to do.

25
00:03:52.972 --> 00:03:55.338
I Watched Which side of the fin tracks
are more indented.

26
00:03:55.474 --> 00:03:56.941
That shoWs Which
direction they're going.

27
00:03:57.076 --> 00:04:00.773
I saW hoW long the drag skids are.
That shoWs you hoW fast they're going.

28
00:04:09.155 --> 00:04:10.782
There's something under there.

29
00:04:25.204 --> 00:04:28.537
It's a cave-in!
Move aWay from the cracks!

30
00:04:56.168 --> 00:05:01.265
Katara. don't go near it.
This is probably some Fire Nation trick.

31
00:05:02.074 --> 00:05:05.066
Just back aWay really sloW.

32
00:05:11.083 --> 00:05:13.244
Katara! Do not hit that sphere!

33
00:05:28.467 --> 00:05:29.957
Uncle. look!

34
00:06:10.476 --> 00:06:11.909
Is he breathing?

35
00:06:15.181 --> 00:06:17.741
Did you see that light
shoot into the sky?

36
00:06:18.384 --> 00:06:19.578
What's your name?

37
00:06:20.653 --> 00:06:24.646
HoW did you get here?
HoW did you get in the ice?

38
00:06:25.491 --> 00:06:27.152
He's exhausted.

39
00:06:28.494 --> 00:06:30.655
We need to get him back to the village.

40
00:06:37.737 --> 00:06:38.726
What is this thing?

41
00:06:43.743 --> 00:06:45.404
It's trying to eat me!

42
00:06:53.385 --> 00:06:55.285
Look. See?

43
00:07:06.799 --> 00:07:08.426
HoW'd you get all the Way out here?

44
00:07:09.201 --> 00:07:10.600
I ran aWay from home.

45
00:07:11.137 --> 00:07:14.732
We got in a storm. We Were forced
under the Water of the ocean.

46
00:07:14.874 --> 00:07:16.603
I see.

47
00:07:16.742 --> 00:07:19.438
It Wasn't very smart. I Was just upset.

48
00:07:20.446 --> 00:07:22.380
- Thanks for saving me.
- Lucky.

49
00:07:22.982 --> 00:07:25.951
I probably should get home.
They'll all be Worried.

50
00:07:26.085 --> 00:07:29.213
- You're not still upset?
- Not as much as I Was.

51
00:07:47.072 --> 00:07:48.198
The Fire Nation is here.

52
00:07:48.340 --> 00:07:50.205
- What?
- And they brought their machines.

53
00:07:52.378 --> 00:07:54.744
Don't come out
till I tell you it's safe.

54
00:07:56.549 --> 00:08:00.508
- Is something Wrong?
- No. Please Wait here.

55
00:08:00.653 --> 00:08:04.145
- Hurry. noW!
- Secure the area!

56
00:08:15.968 --> 00:08:18.061
It can't be coincidence
that We break him out of the ice.

57
00:08:18.204 --> 00:08:21.765
light shoots into the sky and noW the
Fire Nation is here With their machines.

58
00:08:33.152 --> 00:08:35.120
Sokka. don't.

59
00:08:44.263 --> 00:08:46.197
I am Prince Zuko...

60
00:08:46.765 --> 00:08:50.963
...son of Fire Lord Ozai
and heir to the throne!

61
00:08:52.705 --> 00:08:55.265
Bring me all your elderly!

62
00:08:55.407 --> 00:08:57.238
- Papa!
- Move!

63
00:08:57.376 --> 00:08:58.434
Yeah?

64
00:09:02.381 --> 00:09:03.643
Grandma!

65
00:09:08.387 --> 00:09:10.981
Please don't... don't harm him!

66
00:09:12.291 --> 00:09:13.656
Come on!

67
00:09:18.330 --> 00:09:19.991
Katara. don't.

68
00:09:20.566 --> 00:09:23.228
- Form a line!
- Come on!

69
00:09:27.506 --> 00:09:28.700
Here.

70
00:09:29.575 --> 00:09:30.769
Hey.

71
00:09:44.423 --> 00:09:46.118
Grammy!

72
00:09:48.594 --> 00:09:49.925
You're scaring these people.

73
00:09:57.803 --> 00:09:59.862
Who are you? What's your name?!

74
00:10:00.005 --> 00:10:03.031
- I don't need to tell you anything.
- Firebenders!

75
00:10:08.180 --> 00:10:10.045
I'm taking you to my ship.

76
00:10:10.549 --> 00:10:14.383
If you don't come.
I'll burn doWn this village.

77
00:10:15.020 --> 00:10:18.478
I'll go With you.
Don't hurt anyone.

78
00:10:33.906 --> 00:10:36.500
They Were looking for someone old
and they Were looking for someone

79
00:10:36.642 --> 00:10:38.337
With the same markings the boy had.

80
00:10:38.477 --> 00:10:41.742
They dragged Mom aWay
the same Way When We Were babies.

81
00:10:41.880 --> 00:10:45.213
She Wouldn't have Watched us being
taken aWay. She Would have fought.

82
00:10:45.351 --> 00:10:48.878
We found that boy. He's our
responsibility. We should fight.

83
00:10:50.089 --> 00:10:52.785
What Would you do
if they tried to take me aWay?

84
00:10:52.925 --> 00:10:54.415
I'd kill them all.

85
00:10:55.894 --> 00:10:58.522
- Why?
- Because you're my sister.

86
00:10:59.198 --> 00:11:01.860
Because Dad told me
to protect you With my life.

87
00:11:03.769 --> 00:11:08.968
Because I'm your responsibility.
And this boy is our responsibility.

88
00:11:12.511 --> 00:11:16.504
What do you Want us to do. Katara?
HoW are We supposed to save him?

89
00:11:16.648 --> 00:11:19.048
They're on a ship.
We'd need a miracle to catch them.

90
00:11:19.184 --> 00:11:22.176
I knoW you think everything's
going to Work out. but I don't.

91
00:11:37.636 --> 00:11:40.127
His bison creature thing floats.

92
00:12:00.926 --> 00:12:02.052
What do you Want With me?

93
00:12:03.495 --> 00:12:06.828
My nepheW Wants me to perform
a little test on you.

94
00:12:09.168 --> 00:12:12.296
- What kind of test?
- I assure you. it Won't hurt.

95
00:12:12.438 --> 00:12:15.930
I've performed it hundreds of times.
It only takes a feW moments.

96
00:12:16.075 --> 00:12:17.599
And then you're free to go.

97
00:12:19.678 --> 00:12:22.545
Would you mind if I put a feW things
in front of you at the table?

98
00:12:23.182 --> 00:12:25.173
It Will only take a moment.

99
00:12:26.118 --> 00:12:27.745
That's all you Want?

100
00:12:27.886 --> 00:12:31.083
My name is Iroh.
and you have my Word.

101
00:12:32.891 --> 00:12:34.825
Grandma. I knoW
you're gonna try to stop us.

102
00:12:34.960 --> 00:12:37.758
- but this is just something I need...
- Sit doWn.

103
00:12:39.364 --> 00:12:43.460
I kneW from the first time
We discovered you Were a Bender.

104
00:12:43.602 --> 00:12:46.537
that one day.
I Would realize your destiny.

105
00:12:47.439 --> 00:12:52.206
There hasn't been a Waterbender
in the Southern Water Tribe

106
00:12:52.344 --> 00:12:55.245
since my friend Hama Was taken aWay.

107
00:12:56.882 --> 00:13:00.545
Today. I found out that destiny.

108
00:13:01.587 --> 00:13:03.214
Did you see that boy's tattoos?

109
00:13:04.156 --> 00:13:07.557
Tattoos like that haven't
been seen in over a century.

110
00:13:08.560 --> 00:13:12.155
I believe they are Airbending tattoos.

111
00:13:12.531 --> 00:13:14.396
HoW can that be?

112
00:13:14.533 --> 00:13:19.561
I believe that little boy
might be the Avatar.

113
00:13:22.407 --> 00:13:27.936
Once. a long time ago.
the Spirit World kept balance over us.

114
00:13:28.080 --> 00:13:30.105
What is the Spirit World. Grandma?

115
00:13:30.249 --> 00:13:33.275
It's not a place made up
of things you can touch.

116
00:13:33.418 --> 00:13:36.148
But it exists. nonetheless.

117
00:13:37.389 --> 00:13:42.258
It is filled With the most amazing forms
of dazzling creatures...

118
00:13:42.761 --> 00:13:48.358
...that exist in the most
exotic valleys. mountains and forests.

119
00:13:49.268 --> 00:13:53.034
Each of these creatures is a Spirit.

120
00:13:53.172 --> 00:13:55.697
They've Watched over us
since the beginning.

121
00:13:55.841 --> 00:14:00.505
They have guided us. And only
the Avatar can go speak to them.

122
00:14:00.646 --> 00:14:02.375
Aren't there Spirits here?

123
00:14:02.614 --> 00:14:06.448
Yes. there are some Spirits
that live hidden among us.

124
00:14:06.585 --> 00:14:09.850
sure they're Watching us
With great sadness...

125
00:14:11.456 --> 00:14:16.018
The Fire Nation doesn't Wish
to live by the Spirits.

126
00:14:16.161 --> 00:14:19.619
That's Why they're so frightened
by the existence of the Avatar.

127
00:14:20.132 --> 00:14:23.590
- What can he do?
- With his mastery of the four elements.

128
00:14:23.735 --> 00:14:27.637
he Will begin to change hearts.

129
00:14:28.640 --> 00:14:32.974
And it is in the heart
that all Wars are Won.

130
00:14:35.814 --> 00:14:38.806
NoW. go help this boy.

131
00:14:40.219 --> 00:14:41.880
He Will need you tWo.

132
00:14:43.488 --> 00:14:46.150
And We all need him.

133
00:15:48.754 --> 00:15:51.621
You are my prisoner...

134
00:15:52.724 --> 00:15:54.385
...Airbender.

135
00:15:56.662 --> 00:15:58.220
I'm taking you back to the Fire Nation.

136
00:15:58.630 --> 00:16:01.098
- You said...
- I apologize.

137
00:16:01.233 --> 00:16:03.167
I should have explained further.

138
00:16:03.302 --> 00:16:08.239
If you failed the test. as all others
did. you Were free to leave.

139
00:16:08.373 --> 00:16:13.333
But. as it turns out. you are
the only one in the entire World

140
00:16:13.478 --> 00:16:15.378
Who could pass this test.

141
00:16:16.748 --> 00:16:18.978
It is truly an honor
to be in your presence.

142
00:16:20.852 --> 00:16:23.582
Don't even try to escape.
This is a Warship!

143
00:16:28.694 --> 00:16:30.093
Stop! There's no Way you can...

144
00:17:09.201 --> 00:17:11.465
Don't move! You have noWhere to run!

145
00:17:11.770 --> 00:17:12.759
Halt!

146
00:17:13.372 --> 00:17:14.862
Don't let him escape!

147
00:17:15.307 --> 00:17:16.296
Get him!

148
00:17:38.730 --> 00:17:40.493
Thanks for bringing Appa to me.

149
00:17:40.632 --> 00:17:43.658
The Fire Nation is up to something.
I have to go back noW.

150
00:17:43.802 --> 00:17:46.896
- We'll come With you.
- I can take you back to the village.

151
00:17:49.007 --> 00:17:50.167
We're going With you.

152
00:17:53.278 --> 00:17:55.405
You found the Avatar.

153
00:17:57.249 --> 00:18:00.582
For a moment. I had my honor back.

154
00:18:02.087 --> 00:18:07.423
Your destinies are tied. Zuko.
That. you can be sure of.

155
00:18:13.365 --> 00:18:17.358
Aang flew us to his home. He told us
how he left there in a storm on Appa.

156
00:18:17.602 --> 00:18:20.435
and got forced into the ocean
where they almost drowned.

157
00:18:20.572 --> 00:18:23.336
Aang Airbended a sphere around them.
and ice formed.

158
00:18:23.475 --> 00:18:25.943
And he couldn't remember
anything after that.

159
00:18:26.111 --> 00:18:29.444
Hey. Chinto! Monae! I'm back!

160
00:18:29.781 --> 00:18:32.875
Hey. guys! I Want you to meet someone!

161
00:18:33.785 --> 00:18:35.446
This is Where you live?

162
00:18:35.587 --> 00:18:37.782
They must be playing some trick
or something.

163
00:18:37.923 --> 00:18:40.790
Monk Gyatso is gonna try and jump out
and scare me at any moment.

164
00:18:41.259 --> 00:18:43.193
He's the teacher responsible for me.

165
00:18:45.764 --> 00:18:47.391
He's kind of like my father.

166
00:18:48.300 --> 00:18:51.463
- Is it OK if you tell me your name?
- The monks named me Aang.

167
00:18:53.472 --> 00:18:56.134
OK. guys! Enough!

168
00:18:58.477 --> 00:19:01.310
Spider-rat!
They're poisonous! Get behind me.

169
00:19:02.481 --> 00:19:05.143
He's a flying lemur-bat.
We keep them as pets.

170
00:19:05.417 --> 00:19:06.975
Weren't they extinct a long time ago?

171
00:19:07.986 --> 00:19:11.422
Extinct? No. there must be thousands
of them on this mountain.

172
00:19:14.226 --> 00:19:16.160
Your friends Were monks?

173
00:19:16.294 --> 00:19:19.127
I knoW Where they are right noW.
They're at the prayer field!

174
00:19:23.168 --> 00:19:26.501
Aang. Wait! I have to talk to you!

175
00:19:37.182 --> 00:19:38.513
Aang...

176
00:19:39.518 --> 00:19:44.353
...I think you Were in that ice
for almost a hundred years.

177
00:19:46.691 --> 00:19:51.651
- The Firebenders started a War.
- I left a feW days ago.

178
00:19:52.497 --> 00:19:57.366
Aang. the Fire Nation kneW the Avatar
Would be born into the Air Nomads...

179
00:19:58.870 --> 00:20:01.202
...so they exterminated
all the Air Nomads.

180
00:20:11.716 --> 00:20:12.705
You're lying!

181
00:20:13.218 --> 00:20:14.879
You're lying!

182
00:20:26.298 --> 00:20:28.289
This is Monk Gyatso's.

183
00:20:29.234 --> 00:20:30.895
I made it for him.

184
00:20:43.915 --> 00:20:47.316
No!

185
00:21:03.768 --> 00:21:06.532
Katara! Stay aWay from him!

186
00:21:10.609 --> 00:21:11.598
Katara!

187
00:21:11.876 --> 00:21:13.537
Stay away from him!

188
00:21:18.216 --> 00:21:19.808
Your friends were monks?

189
00:21:49.714 --> 00:21:51.045
The Avatar?

190
00:21:52.484 --> 00:21:55.351
Where have you been?

191
00:21:55.487 --> 00:21:56.818
Aang!

192
00:21:57.155 --> 00:21:59.783
You can't bring Monk Gyatso back.

193
00:21:59.924 --> 00:22:03.587
but Sokka and I can be with you
as long as you need!

194
00:22:03.928 --> 00:22:07.728
Don't give up! We can do this together!

195
00:22:08.833 --> 00:22:10.323
Aang!

196
00:22:46.304 --> 00:22:48.033
The banished prince.

197
00:22:50.875 --> 00:22:52.536
Let's offer him lunch.

198
00:22:55.680 --> 00:22:59.275
I Wanted to thank
the great General Iroh

199
00:22:59.417 --> 00:23:02.682
and young Prince Zuko
for dining With us.

200
00:23:05.356 --> 00:23:09.918
As you knoW. the Fire Lord
has banished his son. the Prince.

201
00:23:10.061 --> 00:23:13.224
and renounced his love of him. and Will
not let him return to the throne

202
00:23:13.364 --> 00:23:15.059
unless he finds the Avatar.

203
00:23:16.134 --> 00:23:19.399
The Fire Lord believes his son
is too soft.

204
00:23:19.537 --> 00:23:22.438
and by doing this.
he Will become strong

205
00:23:22.574 --> 00:23:25.566
and become a Worthy heir
to the throne.

206
00:23:26.911 --> 00:23:29.436
I commend the Fire Lord's discipline.

207
00:23:29.581 --> 00:23:33.574
For example. it seems
I need to remind Prince Zuko

208
00:23:33.718 --> 00:23:38.087
that. during his banishment.
he is an enemy of the Fire Nation

209
00:23:38.223 --> 00:23:41.351
and is not alloWed
to Wear the Fire Nation uniform.

210
00:23:42.927 --> 00:23:45.327
But We Will let him Wear it today.

211
00:23:45.463 --> 00:23:47.693
like a child Wearing a costume.

212
00:23:55.774 --> 00:24:00.609
One day. my father Will take me back
and you Will boW before me.

213
00:25:13.518 --> 00:25:14.576
You OK?

214
00:25:16.187 --> 00:25:17.711
I'll be fine.

215
00:25:17.856 --> 00:25:21.690
You knoW. my grandma thinks
because you're an Airbender.

216
00:25:21.826 --> 00:25:23.191
that you could be the Avatar.

217
00:25:26.064 --> 00:25:28.191
HoW much does
the Fire Nation control?

218
00:25:29.367 --> 00:25:32.336
A lot of villages in the Earth Kingdom.
like around here.

219
00:25:32.470 --> 00:25:35.735
They haven't been able to conquer
big cities. like Ba Sing Se.

220
00:25:35.874 --> 00:25:38.035
but they're making plans. I'm sure.

221
00:25:39.377 --> 00:25:40.708
So...

222
00:25:41.546 --> 00:25:43.810
...are you the Avatar. Aang?

223
00:25:50.555 --> 00:25:51.886
What is this?

224
00:25:53.157 --> 00:25:54.283
Stay hidden.

225
00:26:01.399 --> 00:26:03.697
- That child is being arrested.
- For What?

226
00:26:03.835 --> 00:26:08.169
He Was bending tiny stones at us
from behind a tree. It really hurt.

227
00:26:08.306 --> 00:26:09.534
He can bend earth?

228
00:26:10.408 --> 00:26:13.002
Earthbending is forbidden
in this village.

229
00:26:13.745 --> 00:26:17.579
Leave him alone.
You're not taking him anywhere.

230
00:26:18.116 --> 00:26:21.483
No one is taking anybody aWay!

231
00:26:24.989 --> 00:26:26.047
She's a bender!

232
00:26:31.930 --> 00:26:33.261
Katara!

233
00:26:56.120 --> 00:26:57.280
Move.

234
00:26:58.122 --> 00:26:59.282
You. too.

235
00:26:59.424 --> 00:27:00.413
Dad!

236
00:27:04.462 --> 00:27:07.226
- This is my father.
- Hello.

237
00:27:07.365 --> 00:27:11.131
That's the Fire Nation's plan.
suppress all other bending.

238
00:27:13.304 --> 00:27:15.636
HoW did this happen to your village?

239
00:27:17.141 --> 00:27:21.475
Fire Nation sent soldiers.
We fought them and defeated them.

240
00:27:22.647 --> 00:27:27.516
Then they sent their machines.
huge machines made of metal.

241
00:27:27.652 --> 00:27:29.643
There Was nothing We could do.

242
00:27:31.222 --> 00:27:34.248
Those Who could not bend Were
alloWed to live in peace.

243
00:27:34.392 --> 00:27:35.984
if We Were imprisoned.

244
00:27:48.172 --> 00:27:49.332
Earthbenders!

245
00:27:52.844 --> 00:27:58.180
Why are you acting this Way?
You are poWerful and amazing people!

246
00:27:58.316 --> 00:28:02.685
You don't need to live like this!
There is earth right beneath your feet.

247
00:28:04.322 --> 00:28:07.519
The ground is an extension
of Who you are!

248
00:28:10.762 --> 00:28:12.696
If the Avatar had returned...

249
00:28:14.532 --> 00:28:16.056
...Would that mean anything to you?

250
00:28:16.200 --> 00:28:21.137
The Avatar is dead.
If he Was here. he Would protect us.

251
00:28:22.940 --> 00:28:24.373
My name is Aang...

252
00:28:25.977 --> 00:28:27.376
...and I am the Avatar.

253
00:28:29.213 --> 00:28:32.046
I ran aWay. but I'm back noW.

254
00:28:35.553 --> 00:28:38.044
It's time for you to stop doing this!

255
00:28:38.723 --> 00:28:43.717
The Avatar Would have to be an
Airbender. Are you an Airbender. boy?

256
00:28:46.564 --> 00:28:48.225
Leave him alone!

257
00:28:54.572 --> 00:28:56.437
HoW is he doing that?

258
00:28:56.574 --> 00:28:58.633
I don't Want to hurt anyone.

259
00:28:58.776 --> 00:29:02.803
All Airbenders should be dead.
Kill him! Firebenders. positions!

260
00:29:06.584 --> 00:29:10.247
OK! Everybody can help us noW!

261
00:29:33.377 --> 00:29:35.436
Don't be afraid!

262
00:30:13.151 --> 00:30:14.641
Just leave them!

263
00:30:15.653 --> 00:30:17.086
Fall back!

264
00:30:18.089 --> 00:30:20.148
Go! He's an Airbender!

265
00:30:40.011 --> 00:30:44.277
They took aWay any tools
related to bending.

266
00:30:57.929 --> 00:31:01.797
The Fire Nation took this scroll
from a member of your Water Tribe.

267
00:31:03.534 --> 00:31:05.525
A Waterbending scroll.

268
00:31:10.208 --> 00:31:13.939
This is rare.
My mom told me about these.

269
00:31:15.813 --> 00:31:19.271
This Was you When
you Were born an Earthbender.

270
00:31:19.417 --> 00:31:21.885
tWo lifetimes ago.

271
00:31:22.019 --> 00:31:23.418
You came to our village.

272
00:31:24.355 --> 00:31:28.655
Avatar Kyoshi loved games.

273
00:31:28.793 --> 00:31:32.194
I do. too.
I mean. I still do.

274
00:31:33.197 --> 00:31:35.995
A lot of the villages in this part
of the Earth Kingdom are occupied

275
00:31:36.133 --> 00:31:38.226
by the Fire Nation.
like this village Was.

276
00:31:38.836 --> 00:31:42.397
They prey on the Weakest toWns
and villages.

277
00:31:42.540 --> 00:31:44.508
We should go visit
some of these toWns. Aang.

278
00:31:44.642 --> 00:31:47.202
- I need to tell you something.
- What is it. Aang?

279
00:31:48.746 --> 00:31:52.204
I ran aWay before they trained me
to be the Avatar.

280
00:31:52.350 --> 00:31:54.341
I don't knoW hoW
to bend the other elements.

281
00:31:55.853 --> 00:31:57.480
Why did you run aWay?

282
00:31:57.989 --> 00:32:01.254
The day they told me I Was the Avatar.
they said I could never

283
00:32:01.392 --> 00:32:04.327
have a normal life.
that I could never have a family.

284
00:32:04.762 --> 00:32:07.856
They said it cannot Work With
the responsibilities of the Avatar.

285
00:32:07.999 --> 00:32:11.196
- Why can't the Avatar have a family?
- I asked that!

286
00:32:11.335 --> 00:32:14.702
They said that's the sacrifice
the Avatar alWays has to make.

287
00:32:14.839 --> 00:32:18.366
OK. So. What if We found you teachers.
Teachers to teach you bending?

288
00:32:18.509 --> 00:32:20.374
Which element Would you
have to learn first?

289
00:32:20.511 --> 00:32:23.776
Water. Water comes
after Air in the cycle.

290
00:32:23.914 --> 00:32:26.474
Air. Water. Earth. Fire.

291
00:32:26.617 --> 00:32:29.677
But there are really poWerful benders
in the Northern Water Tribe.

292
00:32:29.920 --> 00:32:31.615
My dad told me about it before he left.

293
00:32:31.756 --> 00:32:34.122
It's led by a princess because
her father died.

294
00:32:34.258 --> 00:32:37.318
There are teachers there. but all
the Way on the other side of the World.

295
00:32:37.461 --> 00:32:40.123
- We can get there on Appa.
- That's What I Was thinking.

296
00:32:40.264 --> 00:32:42.357
And maybe We can stop
in the villages on the Way.

297
00:32:42.500 --> 00:32:45.025
start a change in The War
in these small villages.

298
00:32:45.870 --> 00:32:48.395
- Should We try it?
- Yes. We should.

299
00:33:42.660 --> 00:33:45.720
The scroll we had
was proving to be helpful.

300
00:33:45.863 --> 00:33:49.526
Aang was practicing.
but for some reason.

301
00:33:49.667 --> 00:33:52.101
he was having trouble
with Waterbending.

302
00:33:59.343 --> 00:34:02.471
We moved from town to town
in the Earth Kingdom.

303
00:34:02.613 --> 00:34:04.137
We tried to stay out of sight.

304
00:34:04.281 --> 00:34:08.877
but Sokka became concerned
we were being followed.

305
00:34:41.485 --> 00:34:43.851
Sire. I have good neWs.

306
00:34:43.988 --> 00:34:46.354
As you knoW. I conducted a raid
on the Great Library.

307
00:34:46.490 --> 00:34:48.720
- Which most said didn't exist.
- Get on With it.

308
00:34:48.926 --> 00:34:53.920
I found scrolls in the library.
We are deciphering them.

309
00:34:54.064 --> 00:34:56.055
But I believe they may
contain information

310
00:34:56.200 --> 00:34:59.431
as to Where the Ocean and Moon
Spirits live in this World.

311
00:34:59.570 --> 00:35:01.265
With this information.

312
00:35:01.405 --> 00:35:03.930
We could bring doWn
the Northern Water Tribe city.

313
00:35:04.074 --> 00:35:07.771
We could shoW the World
the true strength of fire.

314
00:35:07.912 --> 00:35:09.573
I am pleased.

315
00:35:10.247 --> 00:35:14.980
Well. Commander Zhao.
are the rumors true or not?

316
00:35:15.119 --> 00:35:19.180
Our spies have discovered someone
claiming to be the Avatar.

317
00:35:20.424 --> 00:35:22.358
They describe him as just a boy.

318
00:35:23.861 --> 00:35:25.920
We should set a trap for this person.

319
00:35:26.063 --> 00:35:28.657
We have many Earth Kingdom people
under our control.

320
00:35:28.799 --> 00:35:31.996
I can leave soldiers
hidden in certain locations.

321
00:35:32.136 --> 00:35:36.903
- And my son?
- He had his chance. He missed it.

322
00:35:38.209 --> 00:35:40.200
Let's hope. for your sake.

323
00:35:40.344 --> 00:35:45.213
my son doesn't find this person first
and he turns out to be the Avatar.

324
00:35:46.250 --> 00:35:50.243
He Would return as a hero and.
for all purposes. be your superior.

325
00:35:52.022 --> 00:35:56.083
Well. I suppose it's a race. then.

326
00:36:16.580 --> 00:36:18.241
We're close. Uncle.

327
00:36:18.883 --> 00:36:21.750
They've been moving
farther and farther north.

328
00:36:23.554 --> 00:36:24.919
We're catching them.

329
00:36:29.627 --> 00:36:32.095
There are a lot of pretty girls
in this toWn. Zuko.

330
00:36:33.097 --> 00:36:35.190
You could fall in love here.

331
00:36:35.332 --> 00:36:39.769
We could settle doWn here.
and you could have a blessed life.

332
00:36:42.573 --> 00:36:44.939
We don't have to continue this. Zuko.

333
00:36:47.111 --> 00:36:49.602
I'll shoW you Why We must. Uncle.

334
00:36:52.049 --> 00:36:56.179
Hey. Hey. Little one. come here.

335
00:37:01.292 --> 00:37:03.624
You look like a very smart boy.

336
00:37:05.729 --> 00:37:09.927
Tell me What you knoW about the
Prince. the Fire Lord's son.

337
00:37:10.067 --> 00:37:14.936
- He did something Wrong.
- He spoke out of turn to a general.

338
00:37:15.072 --> 00:37:17.063
in defense of some of his friends

339
00:37:17.207 --> 00:37:21.143
Who Were going to be sacrificed
in a battle.

340
00:37:21.278 --> 00:37:25.806
Then Prince Zuko
Was sentenced to an Agni Kai duel.

341
00:37:25.950 --> 00:37:27.417
but When he shoWed up.

342
00:37:27.551 --> 00:37:31.419
- it was his father he was to fight.
- That's right.

343
00:37:31.655 --> 00:37:34.180
He would not fight his father.

344
00:37:34.325 --> 00:37:38.352
Then his father mocked him and said.

345
00:37:38.495 --> 00:37:41.157
"I should bring your sister
up here to beat you."

346
00:37:42.533 --> 00:37:45.229
Then the father burnt his son...

347
00:37:46.337 --> 00:37:47.827
...to teach him a lesson.

348
00:37:58.349 --> 00:38:00.180
We'll catch him soon. Uncle.

349
00:38:01.285 --> 00:38:03.845
Then We can think
about the pretty girls.

350
00:38:14.365 --> 00:38:15.662
Aang...

351
00:38:15.799 --> 00:38:18.029
Try to keep your Wrist bent.
like it's shoWing.

352
00:38:21.872 --> 00:38:25.899
What's Wrong?
You've really been distracted today.

353
00:38:26.043 --> 00:38:29.911
I saW Sokka's maps.
We're near the Northern Air Temple.

354
00:38:30.047 --> 00:38:33.813
Do you think it Would be OK
if I just visited there and came back?

355
00:38:33.951 --> 00:38:36.715
- I'd be back in less than a day.
- Why?

356
00:38:36.854 --> 00:38:39.721
He had a vision
at the Southern Air Temple prayer field.

357
00:38:39.857 --> 00:38:42.849
He talked to a Dragon Spirit
Who he thinks can help us.

358
00:38:42.993 --> 00:38:45.518
He thinks if he goes
to another spiritual place.

359
00:38:45.663 --> 00:38:47.392
he can get back to the Spirit World.

360
00:38:47.531 --> 00:38:51.297
I don't think that's a good idea.
We started a rebellion.

361
00:38:52.069 --> 00:38:53.900
Try to talk him out of it.

362
00:39:46.724 --> 00:39:48.453
I can't do this.

363
00:39:49.093 --> 00:39:50.219
I need help.

364
00:40:01.472 --> 00:40:04.373
- I guess your talk didn't Work.
- He'll be back in a day.

365
00:40:04.942 --> 00:40:08.571
The Fire Nation is folloWing us. If We
make a Wrong move. they'll catch him.

366
00:40:47.284 --> 00:40:48.751
Who are you?

367
00:40:51.688 --> 00:40:54.020
Why. it cannot be!

368
00:40:54.858 --> 00:40:58.191
I've heard stories. Are you?

369
00:40:58.996 --> 00:41:00.588
My name is Aang.

370
00:41:01.198 --> 00:41:05.191
I cannot believe
I've lived to see your return.

371
00:41:06.103 --> 00:41:10.199
I'm an Earth villager.
but I visit these temple remains often.

372
00:41:10.340 --> 00:41:14.436
The Fire Nation destroyed this temple.
They have ruined everything.

373
00:41:14.578 --> 00:41:17.741
No. no. no. not everything.

374
00:41:17.881 --> 00:41:21.749
You knoW. there's
a hidden chamber of statues

375
00:41:21.885 --> 00:41:24.649
I think you. of all people. should see.

376
00:41:25.255 --> 00:41:27.883
These are all the Avatars.

377
00:41:28.892 --> 00:41:32.885
These are the reincarnations
of you over the years.

378
00:41:35.799 --> 00:41:39.565
The Avatar Roku Was your last life.

379
00:41:42.472 --> 00:41:47.068
NoW. hoW did the Airbenders knoW
you Were the Avatar. little one?

380
00:41:49.112 --> 00:41:50.909
They gave me a test.

381
00:41:51.849 --> 00:41:55.751
They put 1.000 toys in front of me
and asked me to choose four.

382
00:41:56.587 --> 00:42:00.489
They said I chose the same four objects
that belonged to the previous Avatars.

383
00:42:03.694 --> 00:42:06.026
That's When they told me
I could have no family.

384
00:42:07.898 --> 00:42:11.163
Told me I had a responsibility
to the Four Nations.

385
00:42:15.739 --> 00:42:18.503
There's a ceremony
When everyone boWs to me.

386
00:42:20.744 --> 00:42:23.110
That's When I accept my role
as the Avatar.

387
00:42:25.282 --> 00:42:27.045
But When everyone boWed...

388
00:42:30.687 --> 00:42:32.678
...I didn't boW back.

389
00:42:33.123 --> 00:42:35.455
You seem like a nice young man.

390
00:42:36.727 --> 00:42:42.666
You really do.
You Will forgive me. Won't you?

391
00:42:44.067 --> 00:42:46.797
- For What?
- For luring you doWn here.

392
00:42:50.207 --> 00:42:54.303
I have lived in poverty
because of your absence. Avatar.

393
00:42:54.444 --> 00:42:57.880
So you Will understand
my actions today.

394
00:43:19.002 --> 00:43:23.336
I have lived in poverty
because of your absence. Avatar.

395
00:43:29.179 --> 00:43:33.616
I have seen a vision
of the moon turning red.

396
00:43:34.418 --> 00:43:39.549
The Fire Nation has stolen knoWledge
of us from the Great Library.

397
00:43:39.690 --> 00:43:42.989
They are planning
to misuse this knoWledge.

398
00:43:43.126 --> 00:43:44.457
I Will stop them.

399
00:43:44.594 --> 00:43:48.655
You must go
to the Northern Water Tribe.

400
00:43:48.799 --> 00:43:52.394
If they take that city.
more Will suffer and die.

401
00:43:52.536 --> 00:43:54.766
as your Airbenders have.

402
00:43:55.339 --> 00:43:57.739
You must go noW!

403
00:43:57.874 --> 00:43:59.136
Will I stop them?

404
00:43:59.276 --> 00:44:00.607
Wake up. young man!

405
00:44:03.547 --> 00:44:07.608
My name is Commander Zhao.
I set this trap for you.

406
00:44:09.820 --> 00:44:12.721
Don't Worry. I'm not gonna kill you.

407
00:44:13.924 --> 00:44:18.418
Besides. you'd just be reborn again.

408
00:44:18.562 --> 00:44:20.723
and then the search Would continue.

409
00:44:24.201 --> 00:44:27.898
So Where have you been all this time?

410
00:44:29.573 --> 00:44:31.905
And hoW is it that you're still a boy?

411
00:44:35.145 --> 00:44:37.477
I understand that When you freed
that handful of toWns.

412
00:44:37.614 --> 00:44:39.912
you Were very impressive. but...

413
00:44:41.618 --> 00:44:45.247
...you only used Airbending
against my soldiers.

414
00:44:47.257 --> 00:44:49.248
NoW. Why is that?

415
00:45:02.105 --> 00:45:04.573
The Fire Lord and I have a plan

416
00:45:04.708 --> 00:45:09.236
to ensure our reign
and the doWnfall of our enemies.

417
00:45:09.379 --> 00:45:12.439
I am sending a personal message
to the Fire Lord.

418
00:45:12.682 --> 00:45:15.480
informing him
that the once feared Avatar

419
00:45:15.619 --> 00:45:19.817
is our prisoner
and no threat to our might.

420
00:45:56.626 --> 00:45:57.923
Who are you?

421
00:46:00.797 --> 00:46:01.889
Wait! Don't!

422
00:46:02.999 --> 00:46:04.330
Stop!

423
00:46:31.695 --> 00:46:33.026
Fools.

424
00:46:34.631 --> 00:46:38.294
Close the inner gates!
The Avatar has escaped!

425
00:46:47.043 --> 00:46:48.806
Lock doWn the gate!

426
00:46:50.046 --> 00:46:52.378
Lock doWn all the gates!

427
00:47:06.930 --> 00:47:09.330
To the main post!

428
00:47:10.000 --> 00:47:11.160
This Was their practice area.

429
00:47:11.301 --> 00:47:13.895
Go again!

430
00:49:16.159 --> 00:49:18.457
Do not kill the Avatar!

431
00:49:18.595 --> 00:49:20.290
He Will just be reborn again!

432
00:49:21.931 --> 00:49:23.523
Why are you doing this? Who are you?

433
00:49:35.078 --> 00:49:36.136
Open the gates.

434
00:49:37.981 --> 00:49:39.471
Let them out!

435
00:49:55.965 --> 00:49:59.332
- Is it some kind of Spirit. Commander?
- Not at all.

436
00:50:01.004 --> 00:50:02.335
Do it.

437
00:50:52.922 --> 00:50:54.219
What is this?

438
00:51:52.282 --> 00:51:55.274
And hoW did he escape?

439
00:51:57.287 --> 00:52:01.781
I fear that your son
is not only incompetent.

440
00:52:01.925 --> 00:52:03.790
but also a traitor.

441
00:52:04.461 --> 00:52:06.691
Of course. I cannot prove this. sire.

442
00:52:10.467 --> 00:52:12.128
You think...

443
00:52:12.802 --> 00:52:15.965
...my son is this person

444
00:52:16.105 --> 00:52:19.370
the soldiers are calling
the Blue Spirit.

445
00:52:22.479 --> 00:52:23.946
Yes.

446
00:52:29.452 --> 00:52:32.478
Zhao's men Were searching the coast.
looking for you.

447
00:52:33.490 --> 00:52:35.651
They also searched the ship.

448
00:52:36.960 --> 00:52:39.827
I told them you Went
on vacation With a girl.

449
00:52:43.500 --> 00:52:45.627
Where Were you the past four days?

450
00:52:48.171 --> 00:52:49.502
NoWhere.

451
00:52:51.274 --> 00:52:53.071
We have to keep moving.

452
00:52:54.377 --> 00:52:56.402
The Avatar is traveling again.

453
00:52:57.514 --> 00:52:59.345
Take rest first.

454
00:53:00.183 --> 00:53:02.743
It looks like you
Went through a great deal.

455
00:53:03.586 --> 00:53:08.353
When you Wake. We'll have tea together
before We start the engines.

456
00:53:17.700 --> 00:53:19.861
Do not harm my son.

457
00:53:20.837 --> 00:53:23.362
Leave him to his isolation.

458
00:53:24.040 --> 00:53:28.067
You have my word. sire.
I will not harm him.

459
00:53:54.070 --> 00:53:55.731
Zuko!

460
00:54:08.017 --> 00:54:09.917
And what of the Avatar?

461
00:54:10.253 --> 00:54:13.051
We assume he has
rejoined with his supporters.

462
00:54:23.166 --> 00:54:25.600
It has been confirmed
that he's traveling north.

463
00:54:25.868 --> 00:54:29.497
It is my strong belief that he is
traveling to the Northern Water Tribe.

464
00:54:30.440 --> 00:54:35.104
I believe the child Avatar has only
knowledge of his birth element. Air.

465
00:54:36.045 --> 00:54:40.175
I believe he is trying to learn
in the discipline of water.

466
00:54:40.316 --> 00:54:43.547
He's gone to seek out someone
in the Northern Water Tribe.

467
00:54:43.686 --> 00:54:48.589
where they have lived beyond our reach
and openly practice Waterbending.

468
00:55:34.203 --> 00:55:37.263
We arrived at the Northern Water Tribe.

469
00:55:37.407 --> 00:55:40.171
We presented ourselves
to the royal court.

470
00:55:43.246 --> 00:55:46.841
My brother and the princess
became friends right away.

471
00:56:01.364 --> 00:56:04.492
Aang showed them he
was the last Airbender.

472
00:56:04.634 --> 00:56:07.364
and was accepted
to train with the master.

473
00:56:23.386 --> 00:56:26.651
The city knew our arrival
would bring great danger.

474
00:56:26.789 --> 00:56:30.885
And they prepared for war they knew
would come in the ensuing weeks.

475
00:56:34.897 --> 00:56:38.060
The city Was designed
to Withstand any assault.

476
00:56:38.401 --> 00:56:41.837
If We keep them to the courtyard
and the marketplace till night falls.

477
00:56:42.071 --> 00:56:45.131
Where We have the advantage.
We Will succeed.

478
00:56:45.808 --> 00:56:47.571
If We let too many of them
into the city.

479
00:56:47.710 --> 00:56:50.076
their sheer numbers
could overwhelm us.

480
00:56:50.747 --> 00:56:54.513
As many fires in this city should be put
out as possible When the alarm sounds.

481
00:56:54.650 --> 00:56:58.177
We Want to minimize
their bender sources.

482
00:56:59.589 --> 00:57:02.490
I must assign a guard
to be With you at all times. Princess.

483
00:57:02.959 --> 00:57:06.417
Your presence is our inspiration.

484
00:57:06.562 --> 00:57:09.531
I'll do it. That's me.
I'll be her guard.

485
00:57:09.665 --> 00:57:11.223
Nothing Will happen to her.

486
00:57:13.536 --> 00:57:16.004
I had a feeling you might volunteer.

487
00:57:18.975 --> 00:57:21.842
I've heard no word of my son
for quite some time.

488
00:57:21.978 --> 00:57:25.778
- Do you know where he is?
- I've not heard of anything. sire.

489
00:57:25.915 --> 00:57:28.816
I'm sure word of him
will come to us soon.

490
00:57:28.951 --> 00:57:31.715
The Northern Water Tribe benders
are given their strength

491
