by the Moon and Ocean Spirits.
They Will be difficult to defeat.

492
00:57:35.892 --> 00:57:40.056
NoW. if for some reason
the Spirits Were not involved.

493
00:57:40.196 --> 00:57:41.959
that Would be different.

494
00:57:43.900 --> 00:57:46.801
What have you learned
from the stolen scrolls?

495
00:57:47.470 --> 00:57:51.702
We have deciphered the location
of the Moon and Ocean Spirits.

496
00:57:54.477 --> 00:57:59.471
It is our destiny to have found
this information. Zhao.

497
00:58:02.919 --> 00:58:05.353
Eliminate the Spirits.

498
00:58:05.488 --> 00:58:09.982
take the city and We Will have
thWarted the Avatar in the process.

499
00:58:22.438 --> 00:58:23.996
Water is What?

500
00:58:24.140 --> 00:58:26.734
The floWing element.
The element of change.

501
00:58:28.010 --> 00:58:31.173
To master Water.
you must release your emotions.

502
00:58:31.314 --> 00:58:33.544
Wherever they may lead you.

503
00:58:33.683 --> 00:58:36.345
Water teaches us acceptance.

504
00:58:37.353 --> 00:58:40.015
Let your emotions floW like Water.

505
00:58:41.624 --> 00:58:45.924
Aang. Would you like to spar?
You haven't sparred in a feW days.

506
00:59:18.427 --> 00:59:20.054
NoW. use offense. Aang!

507
01:00:13.950 --> 01:00:17.716
General Iroh. I'm glad you could
accept my invitation to join us

508
01:00:17.853 --> 01:00:22.119
- on this historic event.
- Your invitation Was most gracious.

509
01:00:22.258 --> 01:00:25.625
You are a gifted strategist.
No one can argue that.

510
01:00:26.028 --> 01:00:30.965
Your failure in the Hundred Day Siege
of Ba Sing Se Won't be held against you.

511
01:00:31.968 --> 01:00:34.960
Your son died in that siege. didn't he?

512
01:00:36.872 --> 01:00:38.134
Yes. he did.

513
01:00:39.742 --> 01:00:42.768
Again. I offer my condolences
on your nepheW burning to death

514
01:00:42.912 --> 01:00:44.812
in that terrible accident.

515
01:00:47.149 --> 01:00:48.275
Thank you.

516
01:00:56.325 --> 01:00:58.793
I've loved spending
these Weeks With you. Sokka.

517
01:00:58.928 --> 01:01:00.418
Me. too.

518
01:01:05.001 --> 01:01:07.435
Should We see What the ocean
is doing today?

519
01:01:14.176 --> 01:01:16.144
When there is some safety for all of us.

520
01:01:16.278 --> 01:01:19.111
I Will come visit our sister city
in the Southern Water Tribe

521
01:01:19.248 --> 01:01:21.478
and spend some time in your home.

522
01:01:22.018 --> 01:01:23.508
That Would be great.

523
01:01:25.688 --> 01:01:27.451
But I Warn you...

524
01:01:28.457 --> 01:01:32.188
...my grandmother Will ask you
a lot of questions.

525
01:01:39.268 --> 01:01:40.860
What might she ask me?

526
01:01:42.705 --> 01:01:47.699
She'll say. "Why is your hair White.
young lady? You look very odd."

527
01:01:48.711 --> 01:01:52.909
I Would say to your grandmother. my
hair is White because When I Was born

528
01:01:53.049 --> 01:01:55.074
I Was not aWake.

529
01:01:55.217 --> 01:01:59.051
My mother and father could not get me
to make a sound or move.

530
01:01:59.722 --> 01:02:01.747
So they prayed for days
to the Moon Spirit

531
01:02:01.891 --> 01:02:04.724
and dipped me into the sacred Waters.

532
01:02:06.896 --> 01:02:11.890
My parents said that my hair turned
White then and life poured into me.

533
01:02:13.736 --> 01:02:14.896
WoW.

534
01:02:16.739 --> 01:02:18.400
You didn't tell me that.

535
01:02:19.575 --> 01:02:21.566
You didn't ask me.

536
01:02:22.144 --> 01:02:23.907
Only your grandmother did.

537
01:02:29.919 --> 01:02:33.082
I'm sure Zhao Was the one
Who ordered the attack on you.

538
01:02:36.759 --> 01:02:38.420
Any problems?

539
01:02:39.495 --> 01:02:42.862
We have arrived at the Northern
Water Tribe's stronghold.

540
01:02:42.998 --> 01:02:44.431
They believe the boy is there.

541
01:02:46.769 --> 01:02:48.669
Why do you seem upset. Uncle?

542
01:02:50.272 --> 01:02:52.467
Zhao has no sacredness.

543
01:02:53.042 --> 01:02:55.010
Are you sure you Want to be here?

544
01:02:58.447 --> 01:03:02.941
I Will not be alloWed to live in peace
until I bring the Avatar to my father!

545
01:03:03.285 --> 01:03:05.014
Is that not clear to you?

546
01:04:15.357 --> 01:04:16.847
What is this?

547
01:04:18.194 --> 01:04:19.525
Yue...

548
01:04:21.363 --> 01:04:22.955
...the Fire Nation is here.

549
01:04:46.055 --> 01:04:49.218
NoW be sure to keep your uniform
closed up to your neck.

550
01:04:49.558 --> 01:04:52.049
And remember. your Chi can Warm you.

551
01:04:53.395 --> 01:04:54.794
I knoW. Uncle.

552
01:05:07.576 --> 01:05:08.907
Be safe.

553
01:06:11.874 --> 01:06:13.466
Aang needs to ask you something.

554
01:06:14.310 --> 01:06:16.540
I have to talk to the Dragon Spirit.

555
01:06:17.313 --> 01:06:19.304
He can help me defeat the Fire Nation.

556
01:06:20.482 --> 01:06:22.746
Is there a spiritual place
Where I can meditate?

557
01:06:22.885 --> 01:06:27.413
There is a very spiritual place.
The city Was built around this place.

558
01:06:28.223 --> 01:06:30.020
But we must hurry.

559
01:06:49.878 --> 01:06:53.041
Momo. be nice.

560
01:06:55.684 --> 01:06:57.982
To get your Airbending tattoos.

561
01:06:58.120 --> 01:07:03.217
you have to meditate for long
periods of time Without losing focus.

562
01:07:03.359 --> 01:07:07.352
Some of the great monks
can meditate for four days.

563
01:07:23.479 --> 01:07:26.346
- I have to get back.
- I'll take you.

564
01:07:28.917 --> 01:07:30.384
I'll stay With him.

565
01:07:50.739 --> 01:07:51.967
Aang?

566
01:07:54.743 --> 01:07:56.574
Aang. can you hear me?

567
01:07:59.748 --> 01:08:01.739
I kneW you Were real.

568
01:08:03.085 --> 01:08:05.918
I alWays kneW you'd return.

569
01:08:06.922 --> 01:08:08.321
Me. too.

570
01:08:11.860 --> 01:08:13.589
The Fire Lord's son.

571
01:08:14.930 --> 01:08:17.023
You took him from our village.

572
01:08:43.392 --> 01:08:44.950
Who are you?

573
01:08:45.661 --> 01:08:47.253
My name is Katara.

574
01:08:47.396 --> 01:08:50.297
and I'm the only Waterbender left
in the Southern Water Tribe.

575
01:09:11.787 --> 01:09:13.721
- Go for the children.
- Yes.

576
01:09:27.169 --> 01:09:30.002
I'm not alloWed to go home Without him.

577
01:10:08.544 --> 01:10:10.944
The Waterbenders get poWer
from the moon.

578
01:10:11.079 --> 01:10:13.309
They Will get stronger
as the day comes to an end.

579
01:10:15.117 --> 01:10:17.881
General Iroh.
I've been keeping a secret.

580
01:10:18.754 --> 01:10:20.153
And What is that?

581
01:10:20.556 --> 01:10:23.923
In my raid of the Great Library
earlier this year.

582
01:10:24.059 --> 01:10:26.493
I found a scroll that tells

583
01:10:26.628 --> 01:10:29.188
the location
of the Ocean and Moon Spirits.

584
01:10:29.898 --> 01:10:32.492
To meet a Spirit Would be a great honor.

585
01:10:36.605 --> 01:10:38.732
Well. I hope I can give you that honor.

586
01:11:19.615 --> 01:11:20.775
What happened?

587
01:11:22.451 --> 01:11:23.611
What happened?

588
01:11:24.386 --> 01:11:28.345
Prince Zuko's here in the city.
He took Aang again.

589
01:11:41.136 --> 01:11:44.071
We'll just Wait
till everyone's fighting everyone.

590
01:11:45.774 --> 01:11:48.470
Then in the night. We'll slip out.

591
01:11:49.978 --> 01:11:51.969
Aang. can you hear me?

592
01:11:55.484 --> 01:11:57.247
I knew you were real.

593
01:11:58.654 --> 01:12:01.487
I always knew you'd return.

594
01:12:03.892 --> 01:12:06.156
Hello! Hello!

595
01:12:09.064 --> 01:12:12.659
Please. tell me hoW
to beat the Fire Nation!

596
01:12:24.780 --> 01:12:29.046
You are not dealing
With the loss of your people.

597
01:12:29.184 --> 01:12:32.676
and your responsibility
for their deaths.

598
01:12:33.121 --> 01:12:35.851
You are stopping yourself
from grieving.

599
01:12:36.191 --> 01:12:37.852
You are angry.

600
01:12:38.193 --> 01:12:41.526
You must let this go.

601
01:12:42.230 --> 01:12:46.690
As the Avatar.
you are not meant to hurt others.

602
01:12:59.114 --> 01:13:00.376
Use the ocean.

603
01:13:01.550 --> 01:13:04.576
ShoW them the poWer of Water.

604
01:13:04.720 --> 01:13:08.212
Go! Do this noW.

605
01:13:11.226 --> 01:13:15.162
My sister Azula
was always the special one.

606
01:13:15.764 --> 01:13:17.959
She Was a Firebending prodigy.

607
01:13:18.100 --> 01:13:19.727
My father loves her.

608
01:13:28.076 --> 01:13:30.567
He can't even look at me sometimes.

609
01:13:32.714 --> 01:13:34.409
He says I'm like my mother.

610
01:14:27.335 --> 01:14:29.462
I advise that you
pull back your men soon.

611
01:14:29.604 --> 01:14:32.573
They Will be trapped in the city
When the moon's poWer comes out.

612
01:14:32.707 --> 01:14:35.608
Do not Worry about the moon's poWer.
General Iroh.

613
01:14:35.744 --> 01:14:37.837
Why should you not be Worried
about the moon's poWer?

614
01:14:37.979 --> 01:14:40.140
Because your brother.
Fire Lord Ozai. and I

615
01:14:40.382 --> 01:14:44.216
have decided it is in our best
interests to kill the Moon Spirit.

616
01:14:45.320 --> 01:14:46.480
What?

617
01:16:08.069 --> 01:16:10.560
Calm doWn. We'll find him.

618
01:16:53.114 --> 01:16:56.345
Are you OK?
Did the Spirits tell you anything?

619
01:16:56.484 --> 01:17:00.443
Yes. The Dragon Spirit talked to me.
I knoW What to do.

620
01:17:01.122 --> 01:17:03.784
Aang. We have to go.

621
01:17:27.148 --> 01:17:29.810
You Won't be killed by Waterbenders
if you stay hidden here.

622
01:17:33.321 --> 01:17:34.982
We could be friends. you knoW.

623
01:17:47.335 --> 01:17:49.235
They're getting stronger.

624
01:17:50.839 --> 01:17:55.173
This is a scroll from the Great Library.
This is our map.

625
01:17:55.977 --> 01:17:58.571
Our World is going to change soon.
gentlemen.

626
01:17:59.280 --> 01:18:01.043
Right there and right there.

627
01:18:24.139 --> 01:18:26.699
See Where they're going!
I'll go join the fight!

628
01:18:49.064 --> 01:18:54.559
They are called many names:
Yin and Yang. push and pull.

629
01:18:55.403 --> 01:19:00.170
May I introduce you to the mysterious
Ocean and Moon Spirits?

630
01:19:16.825 --> 01:19:19.885
Why do Spirits take the form
of such benign things?

631
01:19:20.028 --> 01:19:22.929
It leaves them so vulnerable.

632
01:19:23.064 --> 01:19:24.656
To teach man kindness and humility.

633
01:19:26.701 --> 01:19:28.669
Commander Zhao.

634
01:19:28.803 --> 01:19:32.466
there are certain things
humankind should not tamper With.

635
01:19:32.607 --> 01:19:34.939
The Spirits and the Spirit World
is one of them.

636
01:19:37.412 --> 01:19:39.175
What are you doing here?

637
01:19:39.314 --> 01:19:40.941
Stop. Zhao.

638
01:19:41.449 --> 01:19:45.215
The World Will go out of balance.
Everyone Will be hurt.

639
01:19:46.955 --> 01:19:51.324
The Fire Nation is too poWerful

640
01:19:51.459 --> 01:19:55.293
to Worry about children's superstitions.
General Iroh.

641
01:19:56.030 --> 01:19:59.227
Commander Zhao. don't.

642
01:20:07.809 --> 01:20:09.572
We are noW the gods!

643
01:20:10.478 --> 01:20:11.809
No!

644
01:20:27.829 --> 01:20:30.263
Man all battle stations!

645
01:20:35.837 --> 01:20:38.397
You are too soft. General Iroh.

646
01:20:53.087 --> 01:20:55.681
He's making fire out of nothing!

647
01:21:21.049 --> 01:21:22.880
They're breaching the Wall!

648
01:21:24.252 --> 01:21:26.015
To the front!

649
01:21:46.507 --> 01:21:50.910
As the Avatar.
you are not meant to hurt others.

650
01:21:51.813 --> 01:21:54.907
You must show them
the power of Water.

651
01:21:59.087 --> 01:22:00.884
All is lost.

652
01:22:02.323 --> 01:22:04.757
You have been anointed
by the Moon Spirit.

653
01:22:05.493 --> 01:22:10.226
- He gave me life When I Was a child.
- Then there is still a chance.

654
01:22:11.266 --> 01:22:13.666
You can give your life
back for the Spirit's.

655
01:22:14.269 --> 01:22:18.569
- Don't listen to him. he's Fire Nation.
- Nothing is ever truly lost.

656
01:22:22.010 --> 01:22:27.209
- Is it mine to give back. if I choose?
- There are reasons each of us are born.

657
01:22:28.116 --> 01:22:30.380
We have to find those reasons.

658
01:22:39.460 --> 01:22:43.794
- This Was the reason I Was born.
- Yue. please.

659
01:22:45.133 --> 01:22:47.931
There is no love Without sacrifice.

660
01:22:48.069 --> 01:22:50.936
Yue. What are you doing?
You don't knoW What Will happen.

661
01:22:51.072 --> 01:22:54.508
I believe my life force Will leave my
body and return to the Moon Spirit.

662
01:22:54.642 --> 01:22:55.666
And then What?

663
01:22:55.810 --> 01:22:58.335
My soul Will no longer exist
in this form.

664
01:22:58.479 --> 01:23:01.607
Please don't do this.
There must be another Way.

665
01:23:01.749 --> 01:23:04.183
I can't let you do this.
I'm supposed to protect you.

666
01:23:04.319 --> 01:23:06.446
My people are dying. Sokka.

667
01:23:06.587 --> 01:23:09.351
Those Who are in charge of others
have a responsibility.

668
01:23:09.490 --> 01:23:12.220
It is time We shoW the Fire Nation
We believe in our beliefs

669
01:23:12.360 --> 01:23:14.351
- as much as they believe in theirs.
- But Yue...

670
01:23:14.495 --> 01:23:18.659
I'm scared.
Don't make me any more scared.

671
01:23:20.668 --> 01:23:23.660
I Will miss you more than you knoW.

672
01:25:01.102 --> 01:25:02.296
I killed you.

673
01:25:04.505 --> 01:25:06.564
Come aWay from him. nepheW.

674
01:25:08.242 --> 01:25:10.301
There are too many soldiers noW.

675
01:25:10.445 --> 01:25:13.209
They Will never
let you take the Avatar.

676
01:25:14.182 --> 01:25:16.480
We must leave immediately.

677
01:25:17.051 --> 01:25:19.884
He Wants to fight you
so he can capture you. Zuko.

678
01:25:20.855 --> 01:25:22.345
Walk aWay!

679
01:25:25.259 --> 01:25:26.453
Come!

680
01:25:58.559 --> 01:26:00.049
You stand alone.

681
01:26:00.962 --> 01:26:03.760
And that has alWays
been your great mistake.

682
01:28:01.616 --> 01:28:04.346
Water teaches us acceptance.

683
01:28:05.019 --> 01:28:09.547
Let your emotions flow like water.

684
01:32:13.934 --> 01:32:15.265
Aang?

685
01:33:17.665 --> 01:33:20.327
They Want you to be their Avatar. Aang.

686
01:33:24.838 --> 01:33:26.328
We all do.

687
01:34:02.876 --> 01:34:06.573
Our forces in the Northern Water Tribe
have failed to take the city.

688
01:34:06.714 --> 01:34:09.581
General Zhao Was killed in battle
and my brother has become a traitor.

689
01:34:09.717 --> 01:34:11.912
My son's proven himself a failure.

690
01:34:13.387 --> 01:34:18.654
NoW. Sozin's Comet
is returning in three years.

691
01:34:18.792 --> 01:34:22.421
It Will give all Firebenders the ability
of the highest Firebenders.

692
01:34:22.563 --> 01:34:27.432
the ability to use their oWn Chi
to create Fire.

693
01:34:27.568 --> 01:34:31.766
That is the day We Will Win this War

694
01:34:31.905 --> 01:34:34.738
and prove the Fire Nation's dominance.

695
01:34:35.309 --> 01:34:39.939
NoW you must stop the Avatar
from mastering Earth and Fire.

696
01:34:40.080 --> 01:34:43.072
You must give us the time
to get to that day.

697
01:34:44.084 --> 01:34:48.043
Do you accept this
unspeakably important task

698
01:34:48.188 --> 01:34:49.314
I'm putting in your hands?

699
01:34:55.929 --> 01:34:57.920
I do. Father.
